item.title: Inception
item.description: Inception The goal of this blog post is to blog the creation of the blog and this blog post. Its strangeloops all the way down. To get there, we will be using Hugo, the amazing Go based static website generator. Hugo uses Go templates to generate a static website from Markdown. Hugo is themeable, and comes with no default theme. In this blog post we will be using the Future Imperfect theme.
